description:
Celebrity makeup artist Nam Vo (who works with Chrissy Teigen, Aimee Song, and Rosie Huntington-Whiteley) shares her secrets to #dewydumpling skin, and talks about THOT makeup, glow porn, and how she got her start working with exotic dancers. This episode features a new introduction and Raise A Wand segment, but the interview previously aired (episode 167). We’ll be back next week with all new episodes for the fall season! -- Want more of our beauty podcast?
